Create a Desktop Entry
To make Ghidra easily accessible from your application menu, create a desktop entry:

Create a new file for the desktop entry:

 
 
sudo nano /usr/ are/applications/ghidra.desktop
Add the following content to the file:

plaintext
 
[Desktop Entry]
Name=Ghidra
Comment=Ghidra Software Reverse Engineering Suite
Exec=/opt/ghidra/ghidraRun
Icon=/opt/ghidra/support/ghidra.png
Terminal=false
Type=Application
Categories=Development;Engineering;
Save and close the file (Ctrl+O, Enter, Ctrl+X).
